  "notes": [
    "This study focuses on ethnic disparities in male breast cancer burden and healthcare utilization in Inner Mongolia, China",
    "The study found no significant ethnic disparities between Han and Mongolian populations in most measures except 5-year prevalence rates",
    "BRCA mutations, particularly BRCA2, are identified as important risk factors for male breast cancer"
